{"tid":1575663,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求各位 保護新屋嶺義士","createTime":"2019-09-17T02:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T03:57:48.000Z","uid":299763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"539d9cf65866b23b3dc0ede87f50c728087e2651","tid":1575663,"uid":299763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"我知私了大家好爽 好興奮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">肯做實事未？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解仲未有新屋嶺戰犯既起底？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺輪姦 係咪只係得一單？<br />\n係咪無再持續落去？<br />\n有幾多義士係入面比人打死左？<br />\n<br />\n我地一日唔能夠集中俾壓力呢班人渣<br />\n呢啲無頭公案<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只會越來越多</span></strong><br />\n宜家新屋嶺自成一國 無人介入到<br />\n點解唔起底關心下佢地全家？<br />\n<br />\n有警犬係身邊既你 出分力游説下<br />\n自問自己都睇唔過新屋嶺既警察 出句聲<br />\n<br />\n優先處理呢班寄宿係權力既人渣<br />\n情報戰 能夠改變一切<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老豆揾仔</span>等緊你"},{"pid":"1a9e82cad3ee5590e352c4e207cf018934f27dfc","tid":1575663,"uid":299763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c16fdc7f28949cb5cca0fc9c998ff5b93a5513a","tid":1575663,"uid":299763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7aafb0d1d92a76b45c5c0eb574c53eb49c42dbd","tid":1575663,"uid":299763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:28:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abd71627393908dff50564fe48f235222616d9b1","tid":1575663,"uid":299763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfa2d3ccac1e16e60d5875c412606bab4aebb049","tid":1575663,"uid":299763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:28:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b6167515e98ca0340263173525870e1da9454fa","tid":1575663,"uid":299763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T